Index library
=============

This directory contains the sources of the Index library.

The Index library is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0;
the full license text is at:

    https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Generating Makefile
-------------------
You should have CMake already installed on your machine, before generating Makefile.
Run the following commands:

    mkdir build/
    cd build/
    cmake ../

Building the Index library
--------------------------
Run ``make install``.

Running tests
-------------
Run ``ctest``.
